title: NFL ATL: Week 15 preview
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 15 preview
description:
A room full of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Kevin Patra -- preview all of the upcoming Week 15 action.  Find out who's gone with a bold hero pick and which teams the gang believes could be forked by this time next week.  Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
